                <p>Aaron Judge, the renowned baseball player, hails from Linden, California. Born on April 26, 1992, he grew up in this small city, where he developed his passion for sports. Judge attended Linden High School, showcasing his athletic abilities before moving on to play at Fresno State University, where he further honed his skills.</p>
